{"tid":2456813,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我不會忘記，在香港人有需要時，鄭松泰兩脅插刀。","createTime":"2021-03-22T08:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T08:50:46.000Z","uid":343520,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"93ddd7b8b1f4a28f959b526daf2a1393c76df8f7","tid":2456813,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:00:13.000Z","msg":"我不會忘記，在香港人有需要時，鄭松泰兩脅插刀。<br />\n<br />\n高度的執行力、迅速的決策、秉持初心的付出與參與。<br />\n<br />\n五區公投、全民制憲、永續基本法，以及他以自己能力，提供更多就業機會予同路人。<br />\n<br />\n之後，他頭上是刀，腹背也是刀，不斷被製造話題與問題。<br />\n<br />\n受外界言論影響，經常令他意志消沉，但他又絕不容易被打沉。<br />\n<br />\n晚上見鄭松泰，他多數跑緊步。但是，翌日他又會清晨跑步，整理思緒，餘下的時間，只見他努力找方法解決問題 - 積極地，不抱怨，不放負，不追究，不記仇，把一切孭上身。<br />\n<br />\n在「解決自己問題」和「製造別人問題」兩類人之間，我永遠覺得前者更值得尊重。<br />\n<br />\n我尊重和重視這位朋友，因為，世上只有我們是香港人。鄭松泰加油、熱血公民加油！<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰 熱血公民/熱血時報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/26HTmPj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F26HTmPj.png&h=2c6f1340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3G1vCk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3G1vCk.png&h=0e91b228&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02ba6a48c71da32bad06c93281334971ed9f9759","tid":2456813,"uid":255310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:01:23.000Z","msg":"樓主今日開勁多Po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca55d79b30ab6b706bfd6eabd31e61efb1363f5","tid":2456813,"uid":367153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"樓主記性勁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8570899eb04a9b65e09f113b2e8f996c391b3803","tid":2456813,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ca55d79b30ab6b706bfd6eabd31e61efb1363f5","tid":2456813,"uid":367153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"樓主記性勁好<img src=\"/as